{
  "stem": "7624.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of us, some of the kids went afterward to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was about three kilometers to the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to walk down early in the morning and at night, come back there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a lot up, up the hill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't speak no French whatsoever, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to learn French.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they felt that, for the older like us, the 13 year old-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] excuse me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to come back on something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Paris, was my 13 birthday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to have my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Paris.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were about 15 boys had bar mitzvah in one shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was also a rel-- religious home for the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had also some people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the mayor of that village on the out-- outskirts from Paris, was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was Jewish, the mayor of that city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she came also to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't had much to say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just had our [INAUDIBLE] on the Torah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember she gave us each one a present.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got the [INAUDIBLE], a [INAUDIBLE], and a hammer or a saw, because there was a-- we had to work in the, in the children home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My parents even couldn't come to the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Couldn't get there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I still remember the bar mitzvah my brother had in my hometown, which was elaborate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the relatives came and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I was in the South of France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they decided that all, all the people like us, 13-year-old, should go to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the people in the village were drafted in the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a lot of the work opening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So somebody in the bakery there needed a helper.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
